## Initialization
# Playing around with commands

units lj
dimension 3
boundary p p p

atom_style atomic
pair_style lj/cut 0.5

## System Definition
# Rectangle with two circles 

region box block -25.5 25.5 -25.5 25.5 -50 50
create_box 2 box

region cyin cylinder z 0 0 20 -50 50 side in
region cyou cylinder z 0 0 20 -50 50 side out
create_atoms 1 random 8 123456 cyin
create_atoms 2 random 10 123455 cyou

replicate 2 1 1

## Atom Information

mass		1 1 	
mass		2 1	
pair_coeff	1 1 0.01 4.0	# setting LJ coefficients for 1-1 atom interactions
pair_coeff	2 2 0.01 5.0	# setting LJ coefficeints for 2-2 atom interactions

neigh_modify every 1 delay 5 check yes

write_data initial.lammps

## Simulation settings
# minimization

thermo 10
minimize 1.0e-4 1.0e-6 1000 10000

fix eq all nve
fix le all langevin 1.0 1.0 0.1 123
thermo 1000

dump dmp all atom 100 dump.eq.lammpstrj

timestep 0.005
thermo 100
run 10000
